Furnish your home with high quality rustic furniture found from our online store (https://www.rusticfurnitureoutlet.ca/) which include wood dining chairs, wood dining tables and coffee tables, and more ... 

Rustic Furniture Outlet's warehouse is based only minutes from Montreal in Coteau-du-Lac, Quebec. We offer high quality hand crafted rustic wood furniture sourced from Europe, Mexico and India including: home bars, tables, beds, desks, chairs, armoires, entertainment centers, TV stands and many more items to treasure at the lowest possible price.
